June 21 was a day that i'm sure 6 of us will never forget...shelby's sweet 16 of course! shaina and I had been planning her surprise since january when we first stepped into becca's oh so fabulous limo! We knew her parents wouldn't get her a limo so we decided to! well a couple days before the big event it seemed like everything was falling apart... we didn't have a limo, shaina's mom wouldn't pay, my mom wasn't home, josh didn't have a credit card, cory and josh were complaining about the cost. cory was trying to get a deal on a limo, and we didn't know if larry could come. Shaina and I both broke down and were crying because we'd tried so hard. She had to go to weggies for some things and then cody was going there so I said i'd try another limo company...Excel was a whole lot cheaper than S&S and everyone was happy with the amount they were gonig to have to pay. Even josh and cory stopped complaining and we found out LARRY COULD COME!

We had our "fam" (cory, larry, shaina, and I) and josh come to shaina's house for the limo ride and then we would be taken to shelby's for the big surprise. I had called mr hill many a times to make sure he knew and so did mrs. hill what the hills had forgotten to tell the rest of the fam that yes josh was indeed coming... josh had told shelby that he couldn't come because he had soccer (my idea haha) Shelby had gotten mad at us because we were always texting and calling each other... she accused us of cheating on her haha but it was all clear to her later.

When we were almost at shelby's house we made josh get out and hide behind a bush and then cory, larry, shaina and I watched as shelby came out the door and looked like she was about to pee her pants... well shaina and I watched haha we made the two boyz duck down... cory didn't stay down though... he sat up and looked at larry and then screamed "LARRY'S TRYING TO GIVE HIMSELF HEAD!" hahaha gotta love brothers... Shel entered the limo and then told shaina and I that she thought we were trying to get josh outa soccer and we said we were sorry and we couldn't. We then got into the limo and turned the corner to find josh shelby looked like she was gunna pee her pants again and screamed. It was the best eveerrrr

we took her out for ice cream in canandaigua...shaina and i paid.

Cory and Larry were acting soooo gay it was hilarious! it was a little more than "brotherly love", but it was really funny... josh even started playing a long after awhile, but shelby's cousin tyler ... well i think he's scarred for life now haha

It was all together a very fun night!
